issue.title: tutorial on how to create a new model and contribute through gazebo_models repo or thepropshop.org

message.raw:
Pull request #425 has updated the tutorial so it's clear to the user that their pull request won't be merged, and clear to us that the pull request came from the tutorial. You can see that the latest declined PRs have been processed quickly.

As for contributing to the Propshop - which has been rebranded to Ignition Fuel, [this](https://openrobotics.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/43000011289-contributing-a-new-model) should be the reference for users.
